# EcoTrack - Tourist Carbon Footprint Dashboard

## Overview
EcoTrack is a web application that helps tourists calculate their carbon footprint based on transportation, accommodation, food, shopping, and activities.

## Features
- Carbon Footprint Calculator
- Eco Score
- Tree Offset Estimation
- Sustainable Travel Suggestions
- Admin Dashboard
- Responsive Design

## Technologies
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- JSON

## Project Workflow
User Input → Carbon Calculation → Eco Score → Dashboard → Recommendations

